text: Livingstone Alleyne (born 18 February 1971) is a Barbadian former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Barbadian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Barbados Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
